---
title: 蒸足系統 — 顧客登入與綁定流程
---
flowchart TD
    A[顧客到達首頁] --> B{選擇登入方式}
    B -->|Google| C[Google OAuth 授權]
    B -->|手機| D[輸入手機號碼]
    B -->|店長帳號| E[Email + 密碼登入]

    C --> F[NextAuth 建立 User + Account]
    F --> G{以 Google email 查 Customer 表}
    G -->|找到匹配| H[自動綁定: Customer.userId = User.id]
    G -->|沒找到| I[自動建立新 Customer]
    I --> J[customerStage = LEAD, phone 待補填]

    D --> K[發送 OTP 驗證碼]
    K --> L[驗證成功]
    L --> M{以手機號碼查 Customer 表}
    M -->|找到匹配| N[自動綁定: Customer.userId = User.id]
    M -->|沒找到| O[建立 User + Customer]

    E --> P[驗證帳密]
    P --> Q[導向後台 Dashboard]

    H --> R[導向前台首頁]
    J --> R
    N --> R
    O --> R

    style A fill:#e0e7ff
    style R fill:#dcfce7
    style Q fill:#dcfce7
    style I fill:#fef3c7
    style O fill:#fef3c7
